    "media:imagetext": "TWA AMBASSADOR SERVICE\nFROM HONOLULU TO LOS ANGELES\nFRUIT CUP HALAKAHIKI\nCHARBROILED HAM STEAK\nLean, Tender and Hickory Smoked,\nGrilled Pineapple Garni\nHERB FLAVORED.SCRAMBLED EGGS\nFarm Fresh Eggs blended with spices\nand a dash of Parmesan Cheese.\nHASH BROWN POTATOES\nLightly seasoned and sauteed to a\nGolden Brown\nCroissant\nPreserves\nCreamery Butter\nJasmine Tea\nCoffee, Freshly Brewed In Flight\nMilk\nTea\n*#173\n= t-\nTWA has pioneered the development of advanced aircraft ovens including microwave units which allows \"cooking in flight.\"\nThis feature enables us to provide you with freshly cooked food in a matter of minutes and assures you more flavorful meals ...\nBON APPETIT!\n80-57\n121",
